SnapTap Pro
SnapTap Pro is an open-source tool designed for mechanical keyboard enthusiasts to replicate advanced input features like "Snap Tap" and "Rapid Trigger".

Features
Precision Input: Optimized for competitive gaming to improve movement responsiveness.

Mechanical Keyboard Support: Specifically engineered for keyboards utilizing magnetic switches.

Lightweight & Efficient: Developed using C# to ensure minimal system impact while maintaining high performance.

Getting Started
To use this tool, simply run the executable and configure your settings to match your playstyle.

